  annote={In this paper, the authors assess the contributions to the
                  pressure field under a nonhydrostatic non-linear
                  internal wave. Their discussion focuses on near
                  bottom waves of elevation, though it could be
                  extended to waves of depression (which tend to be
                  near the surface), and they discuss some of the
